- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper compares the hardware efficiency of different decoding algorithms.
- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) is another possible category as the paper focuses on the hardware implementation of the decoding algorithms.
- cs.ET (Embedded Systems) is a possible category as the paper discusses the practicality of different error-correction coding solutions for communication systems.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with the performance of different error-correction coding solutions in communication systems.
